OL,3,CLook at increasing Scottish Government
OL,4,Cborrowing limits, MPs tell UK
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FA committee of MPs has told the UK
OL,8,FGovernment to look at increasing the
OL,9,FScottish Government's capital
OL,10,Fborrowing limits.
OL,12,FCurrently, the Government is limited
OL,13,Fto borrowing #600 million for day-to-
OL,14,Fday spending and #450 million for
OL,15,Fcapital projects.
OL,17,FBut in a report from the Scottish
OL,18,FAffairs Committee at Westminster on
OL,19,Fthe fiscal arrangements north of the
OL,20,Fborder, MPs pushed for the limits to
OL,21,Fbe increased.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
