OL,3,CLook at increasing Scottish Government
OL,4,Cborrowing limits, MPs tell UK
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FThe report said: "At present, the
OL,8,FScottish Government's limited
OL,9,Fborrowing powers constrain its ability
OL,10,Fto manage fiscal shocks, as it is only
OL,11,Fable to borrow for resource purposes
OL,12,Fto cover forecast errors.
OL,14,F"Capital borrowing limits are
OL,15,Fcurrently linked to, and grow in line
OL,16,Fwith, inflation, which may not
OL,17,Fnecessarily be the highest metric of
OL,18,Fgrowth."
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
