OL,3,CLook at increasing Scottish Government
OL,4,Cborrowing limits, MPs tell UK
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,FIt added: "We agree with the Secretary
OL,8,Fof State that borrowing limits should
OL,9,Fbe linked to the measure which offers
OL,10,Fthe Scottish Government the highest
OL,11,Flevel of flexibility but, crucially,
OL,12,Fwe note that which metric delivers
OL,13,Fthis remains undetermined.
OL,15,F"The UK Government should therefore
OL,16,Fpublish a transparent analysis of what
OL,17,Fborrowing limits would look like based
OL,18,Fon the different metrics advised in
OL,19,Fthe evidence for this inquiry.
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@AOU
