OL,3,CLook at increasing Scottish Government
OL,4,Cborrowing limits, MPs tell UK
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,F"At the next fiscal framework review,
OL,8,Fwe encourage the UK Government to
OL,9,Fconsider reforming the Scottish
OL,10,FGovernment's capital borrowing powers,
OL,11,Fby automatically coupling borrowing to
OL,12,Fthe metric which offers the highest
OL,13,Flimit."
OL,15,FThe report comes at the end of an
OL,16,Finquiry by the committee which sought
OL,17,Fto gauge the effectiveness of the
OL,18,FBarnett Formula ` the measure which
OL,19,Fdictates the level of funding the UK
OL,20,FGovernment sends to Scotland every
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GO]
