OL,7,FThe MPs found the measure was "fit for
OL,8,Fpurpose", although it is "imperfect".
OL,10,FThe committee also rejected calls for
OL,11,Fthe formula to shift and provide
OL,12,Ffunding to Scotland based on need.
OL,14,FScotland, the report said, already
OL,15,Freceives more funding per head than
OL,16,Fany other country in the UK and a
OL,17,Fchange in the framework could see
OL,18,Ffunding cut.
