OL,7,FIn written evidence to the committee,
OL,8,FScottish Finance Secretary Shona
OL,9,FRobison reiterated the Scottish
OL,10,FGovernment's support for full fiscal
OL,11,Fautonomy ` an arrangement which would
OL,12,Fsee powers over tax and spending
OL,13,Fdevolved.
OL,15,FBut the committee dismissed such a
OL,16,Fmove as not being a "realistic
OL,17,Fprospect".
OL,26,@xD@UOUyD@IO]
