OL,3,CLook at increasing Scottish Government
OL,4,Cborrowing limits, MPs tell UK
OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,F"Fundamental questions remain about
OL,8,Fhow full fiscal autonomy would work in
OL,9,Fpractice, and whether it would be
OL,10,Foperable within the constraints of the
OL,11,FUK's current devolution settlement,"
OL,12,Fthe report said.
OL,14,F"Practicality aside, we do not believe
OL,15,Fthat a compelling case has been made
OL,16,Fthat such a change would automatically
OL,17,Fresult in Scotland receiving a higher
OL,18,Flevel of funding."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]vD@AOUzD@RO]
