OL,8,Fappear before the committee, leading
OL,9,Fthe MPs to say "do not see how we can
OL,10,Fconsider this a serious proposition,
OL,11,Fand we remain to be convinced that
OL,12,Fthis proposal is desirable in
OL,13,Fprinciple, let alone workable in
OL,14,Fpractice".
