OL,5,CGovernment
OL,7,F"The decisions we have taken to ask
OL,8,Fhigher earners to pay a little bit
OL,9,Fmore ` while most income tax payers
OL,10,Fpay less than in the rest of the UK `
OL,11,Fmean that we can support vital public
OL,12,Fservices and provide free tuition,
OL,13,Fprescriptions and the Scottish child
OL,14,Fpayment to help tackle child poverty."
OL,16,FScottish Secretary Ian Murray said:
OL,17,F"The spending review provided the
OL,18,FScottish Government with an extra #9.1
OL,19,Fbillion, giving them a record
OL,20,Fsettlement.
