OL,7,F"People will expect that to deliver
OL,8,Fbetter outcomes for Scots ` lower NHS
OL,9,Fwaiting lists and better attainment in
OL,10,Four schools.
OL,12,F"Spending per head in Scotland is
OL,13,Faround 20% higher than the rest of the
OL,14,FUK thanks to the Barnett formula. This
OL,15,Freport confirms that it appears to be
OL,16,Fthe position of the Scottish
OL,17,FGovernment to scrap that formula that
OL,18,Fdelivers higher funding ` they should
OL,19,Fexplain why they want less money for
OL,20,Fpublic services in Scotland.
